OL,3,CPolice investigating arson attack on
OL,4,Ccafe's Muslim prayer room
OL,6,FFootage shows the arson attack on a
OL,7,FBlackburn cafe's Muslim prayer room
OL,9,FPolice are investigating after CCTV
OL,10,Ffootage captured what appears to be
OL,11,Fmasked men throwing "firebombs"
OL,12,Fthrough the window of a cafe's Muslim
OL,13,Fprayer room.
OL,15,FSignificant damage was caused to Cafe
OL,16,FRaha in Roe Lee Park, Blackburn, in
OL,17,Fthe early hours of Monday 11 May.
OL,26,@tD@\rrwD@err
