OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778767871
OL,3,CPolice investigating arson attack on
OL,4,Ccafe's Muslim prayer room
OL,6,FA group of men, wearing balaclavas,
OL,7,Fcan be seen throwing "firebombs"
OL,8,Fthrough the window in a CCTV clip
OL,9,Frecorded at around 2.30am.
OL,11,FFirefighters were called to the scene
OL,12,Fto put out the fire, while police also
OL,13,Fattended and have confirmed an
OL,14,Finvestigation has been launched.
OL,16,FIn an update on their Facebook page on
OL,17,FWednesday 15 May, Lancashire Police
OL,18,Fsay there is "no suggestion" that the
OL,19,Farson attack was "racially or
OL,20,Freligiously motivated".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
