PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778767871
OL,3,CPolice investigating arson attack on
OL,4,Ccafe's Muslim prayer room
OL,6,FA police spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Detectives are leading the
OL,8,Finvestigation and are carrying out a
OL,9,Fnumber of lines of enquiry, including
OL,10,Fchecking CCTV in the area.
OL,12,F"No suspects have been identified at
OL,13,Fthis time.
OL,15,F"While the motivation for the attack
OL,16,Fhas yet to be fully established there
OL,17,Fis no suggestion at this time that the
OL,18,Fincident is racially or religiously
OL,19,Fmotivated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
