FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1778767871
OL,3,CPolice investigating arson attack on
OL,4,Ccafe's Muslim prayer room
OL,6,F"We are aware that incidents such as
OL,7,Fthis can be quite distressing for the
OL,8,Flocal residents in Blackburn and wider
OL,9,Fcommunities, but we would like to
OL,10,Freassure you that is an ongoing and
OL,11,Factive police investigation, and we
OL,12,Fwill provide an update as soon as we
OL,13,Fhave concluded our enquiries.
OL,15,F"We have increased reassurance patrols
OL,16,Fin the area; therefore, the public
OL,17,Fwill see an increase in police
OL,18,Fpresence in the area. If you see our
OL,19,Fpolice officers out and about in your
OL,20,Farea and are concerned, please come
OL,21,Fand speak to us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
